name:String: The v1.1 release may not be ready in time
description:String: Due to some resourcing issues, there is a possibility that we will not make the expected go-live date.

name:String: We may not get enough authors to sign up
description:String: We may not get enough authors to sign up to the platform, making it unattractive to potential library systems

name:String: The database may not support the volume
description:String: We have chosen a low end database platform for this application and it may not be sufficient to handle the number of queries we may receive.

name:String: The book pages may not be easy enough to use
description:String: In our usability testing, there were some usability issues with the book management module, it may result in reduced adoption of the platform

name:String: The software licenses may be too expensive
description:String: Our choice of technology stack may require us to use expensive software licenses which could result in us exceeding the infrastructure budget.

name:String: The client team may not be ready for UAT
description:String: We are required by the contract to do a round of UAT with the customer. We may not have the client team in place in time
